dmca.title: Product Images DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google

works.description:
The image of the Coach handbag in blue.  The URL to the original image, which Coach exclusively owns the copyright to may be found at http://www.coach.com/201009/pairs/looks_09.jpg.

This site also sells counterfeit goods, which unlawfully bear Coach's Op Art (VA1694574) and Horse & Carriage (VA1714051) designs.
